      h4 Dismissing
      p Using the alert JavaScript plugin, it's possible to dismiss any alert inline. Here's how:

      ul
        li Be sure you've loaded the alert plugin, or the compiled Bootstrap JavaScript.
        li Add a close button and the <code>.alert-dismissible</code> class, which adds extra padding to the right of the alert and positions the close button.
        li On the close button, add the <code>data-bs-dismiss='alert'</code> attribute, which triggers the JavaScript functionality. Be sure to use the <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> element with it for proper behavior across all devices.
        li To animate alerts when dismissing them, be sure to add the <code>.fade</code> and <code>.show</code> classes.

      p You can see this in action with a live demo:

      .bd-example
        .alert.alert-warning.alert-dismissible.fade.show(role='alert')
